# 🏸 Court Booking Bot (RA Centre)

An automated Python bot that logs into the RA Centre system and navigates to the badminton court booking page.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Automatically opens Chrome using Selenium
- Logs into RA Centre account
- Navigates to booking system
- Structured for automation and scalability
- Ready for multi-window booking (future enhancement)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python 3
- Selenium
- WebDriver Manager
- python-dotenv
- VS Code

---

## 📦 Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/YOUR_REPO_NAME.git
cd YOUR_REPO_NAME

### 2. Install dependencies
- pip install selenium webdriver-manager python-dotenv

### 3. Add your credentials in .env
- RA_EMAIL=your_email_here
- RA_PASSWORD=your_password_here

### 4. Run the bot
- python main.py